 guests, complete with sleek booths and tables with sweeping panoramic waterfront views. Led by Executive Chef Paul Arias, favorite menu items include the Oceana House Roll, the Harris Ranch Ribeye, and the Striped Seabass.", photoCount: "479.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 13, \"count2\": 29, \"count3\": 46, \"count4\": 149, \"count5\": 939}", email: "info@catamaranresort.com", website: "https://www.catamaranresort.com/oceana-coastal-kitchen", rankingPosition: "5.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 960, \"closeHours\": \"16:00\"}, {\"open\": 1050, \"openHours\": \"17:30\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 840, \"closeHours\": \"14:00\"}, {\"open\": 1050, \"openHours\": \"17:30\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 840, \"closeHours\": \"14:00\"}, {\"open\": 1050, \"openHours\": \"17:30\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 840, \"closeHours\": \"14:00\"}, {\"open\": 1050, \"openHours\": \"17:30\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 840, \"closeHours\": \"14:00\"}, {\"open\": 1050, \"openHours\": \"17:30\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 840, \"closeHours\": \"14:00\"}, {\"open\": 1050, \"openHours\": \"17:30\", \"close\": 1380, \"closeHours\": \"23:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 960, \"closeHours\": \"16:00\"}, {\"open\": 1050, \"openHours\": \"17:30\", \"close\": 1380, \"closeHours\": \"23:00\"}]], \"timezone\": \"America/Los_Angeles\"}", address: "3999 Mission Blvd Waterfront at the Catamaran Resort Hotel and Spa, San Diego, CA 92109-6959", neighborhoodLocations: [], dishes: ["Ceviche", "Cheesecake", "Crab", "Burger", "Oyster", "Shrimp", "Salad", "Waffles", 