wn and seasonal ingredients, our bar and dining areas were created using reclaimed, natural materials. Nothing goes to waste at Civico 1845!", photoCount: "468.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 18, \"count2\": 31, \"count3\": 85, \"count4\": 202, \"count5\": 678}", ownersTopReasons: "{\"sectionHeader\": \"Top 3 reasons to eat here\", \"sponsoredBy\": \"Sponsored by: Civico 1845\", \"topReasons\": [{\"header\": \"The most authentic Italian\", \"rank\": 1, \"image_url\": \"https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/28/bc/0a/a6/fettuccine-ai-funghi.jpg\", \"text\": \"Lovely staff. Wonderful meal. If you are looking for an authentic Italian meal\", \"keyword\": \"authentic\", \"isSearchTerm\": true, \"linkText\": \"Read review\", \"review\": {\"rating\": 5, \"screenName\": \"prettywilson\", \"reviewId\": 603692386}}, {\"header\": \"Full Italian Vegan Menu\", \"rank\": 2, \"image_url\": \"https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/28/bc/0b/34/orecchiette-alle-cime.jpg\", \"text\": \"Great menu for both vegan and non vegan.\", \"keyword\": \"vegan\", \"isSearchTerm\": true, \"linkText\": \"Read review\", \"review\": {\"rating\": 5, \"screenName\": \"DaveR179\", \"reviewId\": 686765885}}, {\"header\": \"Romantic Indoor and Outdoor\", \"rank\": 3, \"image_url\": \"https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/28/bc/0b/33/bar.jpg\", \"text\": \"Nice outdoor seat with a special view of the ocean\", \"keyword\": \"outdoor\", \"isSearchTerm\": true, \"linkText\": \"Read review\", \"review\": {\"rating\": 5, \"screenName\": \"DenaliDreaming\", \"reviewId\": 516052698}}]}", email: "info@civico1845.com", website: "https://www.facebook.com/civico1845/", rankingPosition: "41.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1290, \"closeHours\": \"21:30\"}], [{\"open\": 960, \"openHours\": \"16:00\", \"close\": 1290, \"closeHours\": \"21:30\"}], [{\